<h3>Research Interests</h3>

<p>
<font size="3" face="Verdana">
Authentication and passwords, privacy, usable security, social networking,
trusted computing, malicious software, OS/hypervisor security, identity fraud,
phishing, online banking and PIN security, and Instant Messaging (IM) security.
</font>
</p>

